B. /home/user/reports/summary.log (six lines, Unix LF endings)
TOTAL_REQUESTS: 7
SLOW_REQUESTS: 3
AVERAGE_RESPONSE_TIME_MS: 532.86
MAX_RESPONSE_TIME_MS: 1020
